{"title":"🎮 TOY STORE","description":"\u003cp\u003eDiscover our toy collection.\u003c\/p\u003e","products":[{"product_id":"tarjeta-minecraft-pig","title":"🐷 \"Minecraft Pig\" card","description":"\u003cp\u003eDecorative card individually made using 3D printing in our workshop in Spain. Each piece is printed separately, checked before shipping, and features a clean finish with careful detailing. This model is not mass-produced and cannot be found with this configuration and features in conventional stores.\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"MAKER-MUR","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":53369389416787,"sku":null,"price":1.49,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/1057\/8965\/3331\/files\/20260325_094100.jpg?v=1774879115"},{"product_id":"starscream-transformers-g1","title":"🤖 Starscream Transformers G1","description":"\u003ch2\u003eStarscream — Transformers Generation 1\u003c\/h2\u003e\u003cp\u003eThe treacherous and ambitious Decepticon Starscream joins your collection. This iconic character from the first generation of Transformers is a benchmark for fans of the classic saga.\u003c\/p\u003e\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eGeneration 1 Figure\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eFinish true to the animated series character, with great precision in every detail\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eArticulated, not transformable\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eIdeal for collectors and Transformers fans\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eStarscream Measurements:\u003c\/strong\u003e 18 cm high x 17 cm wide\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\u003cp\u003e🎁 \u003cstrong\u003eIncludes Laserbeak Transformers G1 as a gift!\u003c\/strong\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eTransformable\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eLaserbeak Measurements (cassette mode):\u003c\/strong\u003e 3.93 cm x 5.83 cm x 1.03 cm\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eLaserbeak Measurements (bird mode, transformed):\u003c\/strong\u003e 3.93 cm x 5.83 cm x 1.03 cm\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\u003cp\u003e🔜 \u003cstrong\u003eNew batch and new characters coming soon!\u003c\/strong\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e📸 Actual product images. The final result may show slight variations from the photographs due to the 3D printing process.\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Hasbro","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":53372002304339,"sku":null,"price":49.99,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/1057\/8965\/3331\/files\/DSC_0149.jpg?v=1774900015"},{"product_id":"tarjeta-mustang-p51","title":"✈️ Mustang P51 Card – 3D Printed","description":"\u003cp\u003eCollectible card of the legendary P51 Mustang fighter, individually manufactured using 3D printing in our workshop in Spain. Each piece is printed separately and checked before shipping. Clean finish with careful details.\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"MAKER-MUR","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":53372120990035,"sku":"MM-TARJETA-P51","price":2.49,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/1057\/8965\/3331\/files\/DSC_0141.jpg?v=1774970969"},{"product_id":"dragon-flexible","title":"🐉 Flexible Dragon","description":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eFlexible Dragon\u003c\/strong\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eA 3D-printed articulated dragon with flexible parts that allow it to be moved and positioned as desired. A figure with a detailed finish and refined aesthetics, ideal for collectors and dragon lovers.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e3D printed with precise finish on every scale\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eArticulated and flexible, can be moved and posed\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003csp